\## Academic Scope



This repository supports graduate-level work in:



\- Corporate Finance \& Valuation  

\- Capital Budgeting and Investment Decision-Making  

\- Cost of Capital and Risk Analysis  

\- Financial Statement Analysis  

\- Strategy and Financial Governance  



All materials are developed within the academic framework of the \*\*VEMBA program\*\* and emphasize clarity, rigor, and applicability to real-world business contexts.



\---



\## Project Workflow



Most projects in this repository follow a staged finance workflow:



1\. \*\*Memo\*\* вЂ” Executive framing of the problem or decision  

2\. \*\*Specification\*\* вЂ” Assumptions, methodology, and analytical plan  

3\. \*\*Model Build\*\* вЂ” Excel-based financial model  

4\. \*\*Validation\*\* вЂ” Reasonableness checks and sensitivity analysis  

5\. \*\*Final Deliverable\*\* вЂ” Clear recommendations and presentation-ready output  



Each stage is documented and version-controlled to preserve analytical intent and decision traceability.



